des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your air purifiers , Such as: pureAir Active HEPA+. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:

(1). Download our GreenTech Connect app in app market then register an account;

(2). Configure our devices in our “GreenTech Connect” app and change appropriate name for your devices;

(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, IOS or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;

(4). Search GreenTech Connect skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;

(5). Enable GreenTech Connect skill, and you'll be navigated to GreenTech Connect login page;

(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;

(7). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:

"Alexa, set purifier to Auto Mode."
"Alexa, set purifier to fan speed 5."
"Alexa, set purifier to Night Mode."
